T1  - Incidence of congenital uterine abnormalities in polycystic ovarian syndrome (CONUTA Study).
DO  - https://dx.doi.org/10.1016/j.ejogrb.2022.02.012
A1  - Aslan, Kiper
A1  - Albayrak, Ozge
A1  - Orhaner, Aylin
