T1  - Comparison of sonohysterography to hysterosalpingogram for tubal patency assessment in a multicenter fertility treatment trial among women with polycystic ovary syndrome.
DO  - https://dx.doi.org/10.1007/s10815-018-1306-2
A1  - Christianson, Mindy S
A1  - Legro, Richard S
A1  - Jin, Susan
A1  - Eisenberg, Esther
A1  - Diamond, Michael P
A1  - Hansen, Karl R
A1  - Vitek, Wendy
A1  - Styer, Aaron K
