T1  - Relationship between serum anti-Mullerian hormone and clinical parameters in polycystic ovary syndrome.
DO  - https://dx.doi.org/10.1507/endocrj.EJ16-0501
A1  - Matsuzaki, Toshiya
A1  - Munkhzaya, Munkhsaikhan
A1  - Iwasa, Takeshi
A1  - Tungalagsuvd, Altankhuu
