T1  - Follicle number, not assessments of the ovarian stroma, represents the best ultrasonographic marker of polycystic ovary syndrome.
T3  - Comment in: Fertil Steril. 2014 Jan;101(1):49-50 PMID: 24238271 [https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/24238271] Comment in: Fertil Steril. 2014 Apr;101(4):e25 PMID: 24534278 [https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/24534278] Comment in: Fertil Steril. 2014 Apr;101(4):e26 PMID: 24534284 [https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/24534284]
DO  - https://dx.doi.org/10.1016/j.fertnstert.2013.10.001
A1  - Christ, Jacob P
