T1  - Characteristics of 250 reproductive-aged polycystic ovary syndrome Thai women at Siriraj Hospital.
A1  - Wongwananuruk, Thanyarat
A1  - Indhavivadhana, Suchada
A1  - Rattanachaiyanont, Manee
A1  - Techatraisak, Kitirat
